{"tid":464183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格：喜歡足球自然喜歡睇美斯","createTime":"2017-11-10T09:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T12:32:00.000Z","uid":581,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"055edf68428073b43c5e61eb12d75b4458464c1b","tid":464183,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:35:55.000Z","msg":"對於阿根廷驚險殺入世界盃，雲格明言高興，更表明美斯會令賽事生色不少：「個人來說我很高興看到美斯能參與世界盃。如果你喜歡足球，也一定會喜歡看美斯。如你喜歡足球，也會喜歡阿根廷。他們永遠有頂級的進攻球員在陣，整體來說，如果阿根廷無緣世界盃我會很傷心。」<br />\n<br />\n雲格又指歐洲強球出線世界盃的難度要比南美球隊較低，他解釋：「在歐洲我們有點被寵壞，因為有13個名額可以出線。在小組我們會面對一些弱旅，故不會太難應付。當然這除了荷蘭一組，因為除了法國之外還有瑞典，但整體而言大部份勁旅也不難出線。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=547ec2e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"f793a59957e9c8edf5ffff883809a1c02beee61d","tid":464183,"uid":43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba7aca4d267a698e7d702111b22924a2e816ebc","tid":464183,"uid":5549,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:42:32.000Z","msg":"喜歡足球自然討厭雲加"},{"pid":"537dbc3b61e2f748abc45c313581013d145acb00","tid":464183,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喜歡足球自然討厭雲加</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5935a779ffa214766728c45d31856a2561f3957","tid":464183,"uid":128100,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"中意足球自然喜歡睇阿記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6108b12d759895785461eb074f31aa3053ffaf3","tid":464183,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喜歡<del>足球</del>冠軍自然討厭雲加</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e9dd4d174c60d72f61c715c